1. Environment
	- Rails 6.1.3
	- Ruby 3.0.0
	- MySQL
	- NodeJS

2. How to
	- Importing the database from the file books_development.sql
	- Bundle install
	- Install webpacker
		+ rails webpacker:install -n
		+ yarn install
	- Solr
		+ rails generate sunspot_rails:install
		+ bundle exec rake sunspot:solr:start
		+ bundle exec rake sunspot:reindex
	- Start Puma

